{"tid":1756903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］20個連登仔參選區議會好似差不多全部贏晒","createTime":"2019-11-26T08:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T09:21:13.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b653507b63c2856ab1f84f7482e53bc25c6626d2","tid":1756903,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"之前話有20-30個連登仔參選，想知係咪都差不多贏晒呀？<br />\n<br />\nNow : 二，三十個連登仔準備參選區議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495150</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/features/hottopic/hk-map-11222019052855.html/?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Ffeatures%2Fhottopic%2Fhk-map-11222019052855.html%2F%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0z2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=084f701c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/features/hottopic/hk-map-11222019052855.html/?encoding=traditional</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59852586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59852586&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV0z2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=d7391741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59852586&h=20e533dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59852586</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知既係天水圍同元朗好多都係連登仔贏晒<br />\n<br />\n劉肇軒，楊思健同仇栩欣都贏⋯<br />\n<br />\n係咪100%贏晒呀？"},{"pid":"a691a4204f527e4b1983114bc11f220caceaf6d5","tid":1756903,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"仇栩欣都係連登架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9025e82e1260d3f93f590d500c54d3e35422f","tid"